The paper deals with zero-shot learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves the use of additional semantic knowledge, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the experimental evaluation involves image datasets, which could be considered multimedia (cs.MM).
